All Implemented Interfaces:
JsonCollection
public class ComposerPackage
extends DistributedPackage

Represents a composer package. The source can either be a composer.json file or a json response from packagist.org. See JsonEntity.fromJson(java.lang.Object) / #fromPackagist for details.

Author:
Robert Gruendler , Thomas Gossmann
See Also:
http://getcomposer.org
